## 7. Quick checklist for any DB change

- [ ] Wrote a new `schema_*_<description>.sql` file using `IF NOT EXISTS` / `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING`
- [ ] Added `COPY` line in `docker/Dockerfile.postgres` (renumbered `init-db.sh` if needed)
- [ ] Added path to `MIGRATIONS` array in `local_deploy.sh::apply_migrations()`
- [ ] Applied to QA via `./local_deploy.sh -qa` — verified column exists
- [ ] Re-ran `./local_deploy.sh -qa` — confirmed NOTICE-only, no errors
- [ ] Updated any backend router SELECTs / INSERTs that need the new column
- [ ] Updated solver-side dict builders if solver populates the column
- [ ] Documented the change in `solver_v2/planner_dev/holistic_reports_README.md` fix queue
- [ ] Documented deploy steps in `solver_v2/planner_dev/deployment_notes-<date>.md`

